&lt;h3 id="Loading-raw-data-into-data-frames"&gt;Loading raw data into data frames&lt;a class="anchor-link" href="#Loading-raw-data-into-data-frames"&gt;&amp;#182;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
